menambah jumlah petugas keamanan.

274
00:19:35,270 --> 00:19:38,680
Jadi, Tuan Detektif tak perlu
bersusah payah lagi.

275
00:19:39,050 --> 00:19:41,990
Kalau begitu, kami pamit dulu.

276
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:42,610
Hei?

277
00:19:42,610 --> 00:19:43,300
Ya.

278
00:19:47,590 --> 00:19:48,230
