Bukan, bukan. Keluarga Mori
benar-benar hebat.

291
00:20:26,860 --> 00:20:28,220
Benar-benar deh, Sonoko.

292
00:20:33,290 --> 00:20:34,230
Kudo.

293
00:20:34,460 --> 00:20:35,770
Kenapa?

294
