aku tak akan memaafkanmu.

317
00:21:35,860 --> 00:21:37,520
Maaf, Tante.

318
00:21:37,550 --> 00:21:38,510
Tak apa.

319
00:21:38,770 --> 00:21:41,020
Kami tak bisa ke arena langsung
untuk mendukungmu.

320
00:21:41,080 --> 00:21:42,010
Semangat.

321
00:21:42,720 --> 00:21:43,390
Baik.

322
00:21:45,820 --> 00:21:48,960
Alhasil, ponselnya tidak terbeli.

323
00:21:49,120 --> 00:21:50,020
Iya.

324
00:21:50,450 --> 00:21:53,470
Kalau begitu aku pergi membeli bahan masakan
makan malam dulu, lalu pulang.

325
00:21:53,520 --> 00:21:56,050
Baik, beli ponselnya lain kali saja.

326
00:21:56,110 --> 00:21:57,490
Ya, sampai jumpa kedepannya.

327
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:59,080
Hati-hati di jalan.

328
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:06,780
Dompetku tertinggal di rumah Shinichi.

329
00:22:07,930 --> 00:22:09,490
Ya ampun.

330
00:22:12,210 --> 00:22:13,170
Shinichi.

331
00:22:14,600 --> 00:22:15,490
Shinichi.

