misteri yang terkenal di dunia, kan?

338
00:22:36,650 --> 00:22:39,410
Sementara Shinichi malah jadi
penggemar misteri yang bodoh.

339
00:22:39,460 --> 00:22:40,730
Kau berisik sekali!

340
00:22:41,190 --> 00:22:44,480
Selain itu, Ibumu juga artis
cantik yang legendaris.

341
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:46,500
Yukiko Fudo.

342
00:22:46,740 --> 00:22:47,980
Aku iri sekali.

343
00:22:48,010 --> 00:22:49,910
Ini kan bukan hal bagus.

344
00:22:50,410 --> 00:22:54,670
Ah, cinta pertama Shinichi
pasti Ibumu, kan?

345
00:22:54,720 --> 00:22:56,270
Bu.. bukan.

346
00:22:56,270 --> 00:22:57,830
Kalau begitu, siapa?

347
00:22:59,730 --> 00:23:02,300
Cinta pertamaku?

348
00:23:02,860 --> 00:23:04,050
Siapa dia?

349
00:23:04,740 --> 00:23:07,140
Cinta pertamaku...

